<H1><A NAME=SECTION00050000000000000000><A NAME=secthowlinkingworks>&#160;</A><A NAME=xref_how_linking_works>&#160;</A>HOW HTX LINKING WORKS</A></H1>
<P>
This section describes the processes that occur when a set of
<A HREF="node4.html#secthypertextdocuments">hypertext documents</A> is linked. It is intended to clarify the
messages that appear and to give some background information to help
solve problems and avoid inefficiencies.
